Interface ILPAttributeListener


  • public interface ILPAttributeListener

    2.3.0
    Version:
    2.3.0

    • Method Detail

      • onUpdateFailure

        void onUpdateFailure(Map<String,ILPAttributeValue<?>> attrs,
                   ILPError error)
        Notifies this listener of a failed update.
        Parameters:
        attrs - the attributes that were submitted in the failed update (should never be null)
        error - the error that caused the failure (should never be null)

      • onUpdateSuccess

        void onUpdateSuccess(Map<String,ILPAttributeValue<?>> attrs)
        Notifies this listener of a successful update.
        Parameters:
        attrs - the attributes that were submitted successfully in the update (should never be null)
